#

Creamy Tomato Basil Soup

40 min
$8.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy

Description

A comforting, creamy tomato basil soup that's perfect for any day.

Ingredients

  • canned crushed tomatoes: 2 cans (28 oz each)
  • vegetable broth: 2 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • fresh basil leaves: 1 cup
  • onion: 1 medium, diced
  • garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • sugar: 1 teaspoon
